Here is a quick summary of your definitions:

Loka	Action/Prerequisite (Your Insight)
1. Pitru Loka	Properly fulfilling your family duties.
2. Svarga Loka	Performing many good, helpful acts (Dhana and Dharma) with attachment to the result.
3. Jano Loka	Being good to all living people.
4. Mahar Loka	Performing great acts of valor, like defending the country or the world.
5. Tapo Loka	Engaging in penance, like the rishis, siddhas, and munis.
6. Satya Loka	Strictly speaking only the truth.
7. Bhu Loka	When your good and bad acts are tallying (balanced).

